DCS_GetMessage
#include Style
#Background wimp 1
Module:	<DCS=>DCS/m>
#Line
#Wrap off
Syntax:	DCS_GetMessage
Veneer:	<dcs_get_message>
#indent

On Entry:
#indent 6
{FCode}r0 = flags
r1 = DCS object ID
r2 = 2
r3 = pointer to buffer
r4 = size of buffer
{f}
#indent

On exit:
#indent 6
{FCode}r4 = size of buffer required (if r3=0)
     else buffer contains message.
{f}
#indent
#Wrap
Purpose:	Method gets the DCS message.